OL,3,CNearly a quarter of teachers drink
OL,4,Cmore alcohol because of work
OL,6,FTeachers are turning to alcohol and
OL,7,Fantidepressants to cope with work-
OL,8,Frelated stresses, a new survey
OL,9,Fsuggests.
OL,11,FNearly a quarter (23%) of teachers
OL,12,Fincreased their alcohol intake in the
OL,13,Fpast year because of work, while 12%
OL,14,Freported using or increasing their
OL,15,Freliance on antidepressants, according
OL,16,Fto a poll by the NASUWT teaching union.
OL,18,FMore than four in five (84%) teachers
OL,19,Fexperienced more work-related stress
OL,20,Fin the last year.
