OL,6,FThe survey, of 11,754 NASUWT members
OL,7,Fin the UK between October and December
OL,8,Flast year, suggests 86% of teachers
OL,9,Fbelieve that their job has adversely
OL,10,Faffected their mental health in the
OL,11,Flast 12 months.
OL,13,FThe findings have been released during
OL,14,Fthe union's annual conference in
OL,15,FHarrogate in Yorkshire over the Easter
OL,16,Fweekend.
