OL,6,FDelegates at the NASUWT conference
OL,7,Fwill debate a motion on Sunday which
OL,8,Fcalls for suicide prevention training
OL,9,Ffor all school leaders, and fully
OL,10,Ffunded mandatory mental health
OL,11,Ftraining in all schools and colleges.
OL,13,FThe motion warns of a "rise in
OL,14,Fsuicide, suicide attempts and suicidal
OL,15,Fthoughts within the teaching
OL,16,Fprofession" and it says the union is
OL,17,Fconcerned the number will rise.
