OL,4,Cmore alcohol because of work
OL,6,FIt adds the pressures of the job are
OL,7,Fleading to "a mental health emergency"
OL,8,Fwithin the profession and teachers'
OL,9,Fhealth is reaching "a crisis point".
OL,11,FAmong the members questioned, 3% said
OL,12,Fthey had self-harmed in the last 12
OL,13,Fmonths because of work.
OL,15,FIt comes after Ofsted has come under
OL,16,Fgreater scrutiny in the past year
OL,17,Fafter the suicide of headteacher Ruth
OL,18,FPerry.
