OL,6,FMore than two in three (68%) teachers
OL,7,Fbelieve that their job has adversely
OL,8,Faffected their physical health in the
OL,9,Flast 12 months, according to an NASUWT
OL,10,Fpoll.
OL,12,FA teacher who responded to the survey
OL,13,Fsaid they had vomited "with stress
OL,14,Fbefore work" and had cried at work due
OL,15,Fto "badly behaved students" which left
OL,16,Fthem unable to teach a class.
OL,18,FAnother said: "My energy levels have
OL,19,Fnever been this low before. I have
OL,20,Fnever felt so anxious and have very
OL,21,Flittle confidence in myself.
