OL,6,F"I feel as though my bucket is full
OL,7,Fmost of the time at work and that I
OL,8,Fmaybe can't deal with challenging
OL,9,Fpupils as well as I would normally."
OL,11,FAnother respondent said: "It is about
OL,12,Fgetting through the day rather than
OL,13,Fenjoying it."
